00:02:01.060 --> 00:02:04.240
[Shadow Detective]

00:02:04.260 --> 00:02:06.870
[Episode 2]

00:02:10.630 --> 00:02:12.090
Why did you kill Fan Kunyi?

00:02:16.030 --> 00:02:17.280
I didn't kill anyone.

00:02:17.600 --> 00:02:18.720
When he died,

00:02:18.750 --> 00:02:21.079
you were the only other person
in the room.

00:02:21.400 --> 00:02:24.930
There are plenty of witnesses to that—
don't even try to deny it.

00:02:26.030 --> 00:02:27.960
That's not direct evidence, is it?

00:02:30.870 --> 00:02:31.910
Then what evidence do you have

00:02:31.910 --> 00:02:33.190
that you didn't do it?

00:02:34.910 --> 00:02:36.430
This time, you won't be lucky enough

00:02:36.430 --> 00:02:37.750
to get away again.

00:02:40.630 --> 00:02:41.960
What do you mean by that?

00:02:45.680 --> 00:02:46.190
Dong,

00:02:49.450 --> 00:02:50.710
you guys go get some rest.

00:02:50.710 --> 00:02:51.840
I'll take over here.

00:03:17.850 --> 00:03:19.650
I'm not here to interrogate you.

00:03:20.590 --> 00:03:22.720
There must be some misunderstanding.

00:03:25.910 --> 00:03:27.190
I didn't kill anyone.

00:03:29.360 --> 00:03:31.420
Fan Kunyi also had a heart condition.

00:03:32.120 --> 00:03:34.650
His medication bottle
was found at the scene.

00:03:34.910 --> 00:03:36.500
The forensic officer
is collecting evidence.

00:03:36.500 --> 00:03:40.100
As for the real cause of death,
let's wait for the autopsy report.

00:03:42.960 --> 00:03:45.490
Why do I always end up
in situations like this?

00:03:50.960 --> 00:03:52.220
Here, have some water.

00:04:05.150 --> 00:04:07.080
Save your fake kindness!

00:04:07.630 --> 00:04:10.430
When I'm at my most vulnerable
and helpless,

00:04:10.920 --> 00:04:13.120
all it takes is a little act of kindness,

00:04:13.240 --> 00:04:15.440
and you get everything you want from me,

00:04:15.710 --> 00:04:16.360
right?

00:04:16.750 --> 00:04:17.750
That's why you wait until she is

00:04:17.750 --> 00:04:21.610
at her most vulnerable and desperate,
and then take advantage of her.

00:04:21.800 --> 00:04:23.730
By throwing her a little kindness,

00:04:24.410 --> 00:04:26.470
she'll offer herself up completely.

00:04:27.920 --> 00:04:30.160
It seems there's a misunderstanding
between us as well.

00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:30.820
Oh, really?

00:04:33.070 --> 00:04:34.480
What I saw with my own eyes

00:04:34.990 --> 00:04:36.450
and heard with my own ears—

00:04:36.630 --> 00:04:37.960
is that not real enough?

00:04:39.730 --> 00:04:41.530
Seeing isn't always believing,

00:04:41.720 --> 00:04:44.310
as demonstrated
by what people thought they saw about you.

00:04:44.310 --> 00:04:46.430
I don't know what happened
between you two,

00:04:46.430 --> 00:04:47.510
but if you're keeping things

00:04:47.510 --> 00:04:48.510
from me,

00:04:48.630 --> 00:04:50.430
you're only
letting Xiang Man's real killer

00:04:50.430 --> 00:04:51.720
walk free.

00:05:03.190 --> 00:05:05.650
Fan Kunyi
was Xiang Man's long-time patron.

00:05:09.560 --> 00:05:10.960
How can that be verified?

00:05:13.280 --> 00:05:15.280
He had a badge from the Joy Pavilion.

00:05:18.830 --> 00:05:19.640
[Registration]

00:05:30.270 --> 00:05:30.950
Take care.

00:05:32.270 --> 00:05:32.750
Dong,

00:05:39.070 --> 00:05:40.270
how was she emotionally

00:05:40.270 --> 00:05:41.670
during the questioning?

00:05:43.040 --> 00:05:43.950
Quite calm.

00:05:44.159 --> 00:05:45.510
She only became slightly agitated
when Lu Yizhen

00:05:45.510 --> 00:05:46.370
was brought up.

00:05:48.240 --> 00:05:49.600
Have someone keep an eye on her.

00:05:49.600 --> 00:05:50.330
Understood.

00:05:50.890 --> 00:05:52.280
[Chongde University]

00:05:52.280 --> 00:05:54.390
So, Fan Kunyi's wife is also a professor

00:05:54.390 --> 00:05:55.630
here at the university?

00:05:55.630 --> 00:05:56.360
Yes, indeed.

00:05:56.600 --> 00:05:58.730
She's with our chemistry department—

00:05:59.280 --> 00:06:01.050
a very dedicated professor.

00:06:02.190 --> 00:06:03.720
What was their relationship like?

00:06:03.720 --> 00:06:05.040
I never once saw them

00:06:05.830 --> 00:06:07.160
have a single argument.

00:06:07.310 --> 00:06:08.240
They were always

00:06:08.450 --> 00:06:10.910
deferential and considerate to each other—

00:06:11.190 --> 00:06:13.450
a model couple we all envied a great deal.

00:06:15.480 --> 00:06:16.340
But then again,

00:06:16.950 --> 00:06:18.510
what goes on behind closed doors

00:06:18.510 --> 00:06:21.120
in a marriage—who can truly know?

00:06:22.120 --> 00:06:24.120
What do you mean by that, President?

00:06:27.880 --> 00:06:29.760
Well, once on a weekend

00:06:30.050 --> 00:06:32.600
when I returned to campus
to pick something up,

00:06:32.600 --> 00:06:35.310
I happened to pass
by Professor Huang's office

00:06:36.230 --> 00:06:38.190
and heard what sounded

00:06:38.210 --> 00:06:40.610
like a frantic and heated argument inside.

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:42.190
To be fair,

00:06:43.010 --> 00:06:44.670
professionally, both of them

00:06:45.120 --> 00:06:47.159
have always been role models

00:06:47.159 --> 00:06:48.890
for every faculty member here.

00:06:48.960 --> 00:06:52.150
Professor Huang
is also extremely dedicated—

00:06:52.720 --> 00:06:54.870
she practically lives in the lab.

00:06:56.240 --> 00:06:57.700
She's in the lab every day?

00:06:57.830 --> 00:06:58.630
That's right.

00:06:59.420 --> 00:07:00.510
[Shanghai Police Station]

00:07:00.510 --> 00:07:01.680
I just knew you'd still be here.

00:07:01.680 --> 00:07:02.940
I've got new findings.

00:07:03.040 --> 00:07:05.570
Fan Kunyi's death wasn't
due to a simple heart attack—

00:07:05.570 --> 00:07:06.950
there was another cause.

00:07:06.950 --> 00:07:07.720
Correct.

00:07:07.870 --> 00:07:09.120
We found a significant amount

00:07:09.120 --> 00:07:10.950
of sodium azide in Fan Kunyi's body.

00:07:10.950 --> 00:07:11.560
It is

00:07:11.560 --> 00:07:13.560
a chemical that has only
become available recently,

00:07:13.560 --> 00:07:15.220
often used as a preservative.

00:07:15.360 --> 00:07:17.320
It's colorless and odorless
at room temperature,

00:07:17.320 --> 00:07:18.320
yet highly toxic—

00:07:18.800 --> 00:07:19.950
just a few grams

00:07:20.120 --> 00:07:20.750
could kill

00:07:20.750 --> 00:07:22.360
an adult male like Fan Kunyi.

00:07:23.420 --> 00:07:24.330
What's more,

00:07:24.830 --> 00:07:28.760
the presentation very closely resembles
that of a fatal heart attack.

00:07:29.330 --> 00:07:31.600
Given Fan Kunyi's pre-existing
heart condition,

00:07:31.600 --> 00:07:32.860
lacing his medication

00:07:33.240 --> 00:07:34.120
with sodium azide meant

00:07:34.120 --> 00:07:35.830
that his sudden death

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:38.630
after taking it

00:07:38.920 --> 00:07:41.050
would appear entirely unsuspicious.

00:07:42.159 --> 00:07:43.760
That's downright sinister.

00:07:44.950 --> 00:07:46.159
But

00:07:46.430 --> 00:07:47.040
sodium azide

00:07:47.040 --> 00:07:49.100
is an extremely hazardous chemical—

00:07:49.390 --> 00:07:50.320
ordinary people

00:07:50.630 --> 00:07:53.890
wouldn't have an opportunity
to come into contact with it.

00:07:55.310 --> 00:07:55.800
Dong,

00:07:56.630 --> 00:07:57.830
time to close the net.

00:08:00.630 --> 00:08:01.430
Inspector,

00:08:02.100 --> 00:08:03.830
have we identified the killer?

00:08:17.100 --> 00:08:18.920
You're a professor
in the chemistry department,

00:08:18.920 --> 00:08:19.480
correct?

00:08:22.270 --> 00:08:22.680
Yes.

00:08:24.240 --> 00:08:25.000
So what?

00:08:28.160 --> 00:08:29.600
We've found a discrepancy

00:08:29.600 --> 00:08:31.240
in the recorded amount of sodium azide

00:08:31.240 --> 00:08:32.600
in the university lab.

00:08:34.000 --> 00:08:36.059
Do you have any explanation for this?

00:08:36.080 --> 00:08:37.630
I have nothing to explain.

00:08:38.440 --> 00:08:39.840
I know nothing about it.

00:08:53.150 --> 00:08:54.960
You know what this is, don't you?

00:08:56.440 --> 00:08:57.670
Joy Pavilion—

00:08:58.360 --> 00:09:00.200
it's not unfamiliar to you, is it?

00:09:00.200 --> 00:09:01.720
You're the one
who caused scenes at the Joy Pavilion

00:09:01.720 --> 00:09:03.050
multiple times, right?

00:09:05.630 --> 00:09:07.830
I don't know
what you're talking about.

00:09:10.130 --> 00:09:10.790
No problem.

00:09:12.030 --> 00:09:13.490
Let me spell it out for you.

00:09:15.030 --> 00:09:16.150
Joy Pavilion

00:09:16.720 --> 00:09:17.960
is a "Shuyu"—

00:09:18.840 --> 00:09:20.570
a high-class courtesan house.

00:09:20.870 --> 00:09:22.440
Their services are expensive,

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:23.840
and a small badge like this

00:09:23.840 --> 00:09:25.270
costs a fortune.

00:09:25.290 --> 00:09:27.720
Just how much of your family's savings
did your husband spend

00:09:27.720 --> 00:09:29.360
to get such a badge?

00:09:30.790 --> 00:09:31.630
Stop it!

00:09:31.700 --> 00:09:33.700
All those nights he never came home—

00:09:34.080 --> 00:09:35.240
you thought he was

00:09:35.240 --> 00:09:36.270
diligently preparing lessons at school,

00:09:36.270 --> 00:09:38.080
but he was out there paying for pleasure.

00:09:38.080 --> 00:09:39.310
Enough! I said enough!

00:09:39.310 --> 00:09:40.310
One more thing:

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:43.270
the woman he was seeing
at the Joy Pavilion

00:09:43.270 --> 00:09:44.400
was his own student—

00:09:44.770 --> 00:09:46.300
someone you probably know.

00:09:46.820 --> 00:09:49.440
By day, they were teacher and student,
but at night...

00:09:49.440 --> 00:09:50.790
Do you think he ever
spared a single thought

00:09:50.790 --> 00:09:52.220
for you while doing all this?

00:09:52.220 --> 00:09:52.930
Stop!

00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:55.510
Don't say another word!

00:09:56.320 --> 00:09:57.520
They deserved to die!

00:09:57.600 --> 00:09:58.840
Every last one of them!

00:09:58.840 --> 00:09:59.970
So you poisoned him?

00:10:00.200 --> 00:10:01.000
That's right.

00:10:02.670 --> 00:10:03.750
That bastard

00:10:04.270 --> 00:10:05.930
spent our entire life savings

00:10:06.080 --> 00:10:07.270
on that whore,

00:10:07.270 --> 00:10:09.070
without a single thought for me!

00:10:10.750 --> 00:10:12.000
I'm so full of regret—

00:10:12.860 --> 00:10:13.780
I should have

00:10:14.270 --> 00:10:16.750
tormented him more before letting him die!

00:10:18.920 --> 00:10:20.450
So you killed Xiang Man too?

00:10:22.260 --> 00:10:23.260
Xiang Man?

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:26.480
Why would I kill her?

00:10:28.000 --> 00:10:30.200
The one who deserved to die is Lu Yizhen!

00:10:31.840 --> 00:10:32.840
If I'd known

00:10:32.840 --> 00:10:34.910
she was involved with that scum,

00:10:37.120 --> 00:10:39.850
I would have made sure
she suffered the same fate!

00:10:49.630 --> 00:10:51.230
You've got the wrong person.

00:10:52.510 --> 00:10:54.170
Fan Kunyi went to Joy Pavilion

00:10:54.960 --> 00:10:56.030
to see Xiang Man.

00:10:59.150 --> 00:11:00.080
What did you say?

00:11:07.630 --> 00:11:09.080
So Xiang Man's killer

00:11:09.870 --> 00:11:11.330
is someone else entirely?

00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:30.040
Lu Yizhen.

00:11:33.320 --> 00:11:35.120
The real culprit has been caught.

00:11:35.120 --> 00:11:36.450
You got what you wanted.

00:11:36.870 --> 00:11:40.080
From now on, let's go our separate ways
and leave each other alone.

00:11:40.080 --> 00:11:43.010
To be precise,
we've only caught one of the culprits.

00:11:43.470 --> 00:11:44.800
What do you mean by that?

00:11:47.200 --> 00:11:48.480
A further autopsy

00:11:48.790 --> 00:11:50.270
confirmed that Fan Kunyi and Xiang Man

00:11:50.270 --> 00:11:52.070
died of sodium azide poisoning.

00:11:52.120 --> 00:11:53.030
Sodium azide

00:11:53.030 --> 00:11:54.480
is a highly toxic chemical—

00:11:54.480 --> 00:11:57.810
its poisoning symptoms
closely resemble those of a heart attack.

00:11:57.810 --> 00:12:00.270
Huang Tinghui
discovered Fan Kunyi's affairs,

00:12:00.270 --> 00:12:01.480
stole sodium azide

00:12:01.480 --> 00:12:02.670
from the university lab,

00:12:02.670 --> 00:12:04.870
and laced his heart medication with it.

00:12:06.440 --> 00:12:07.390
So you're saying...

00:12:07.390 --> 00:12:09.200
when I met Fan Kunyi,

00:12:09.200 --> 00:12:11.460
he had already taken the poisoned pills?

00:12:12.500 --> 00:12:13.030
Correct.

00:12:15.390 --> 00:12:17.240
Then what did you mean by

00:12:17.240 --> 00:12:18.200
"only caught one of the culprits"?

00:12:18.200 --> 00:12:20.460
Are you saying she didn't kill Xiang Man?

00:12:21.930 --> 00:12:22.930
We're not sure.

00:12:23.390 --> 00:12:25.720
Huang Tinghui hasn't confessed
to Xiang Man's murder.

00:12:25.720 --> 00:12:27.030
Moreover, according to the lab records,

00:12:27.030 --> 00:12:28.380
the amount of sodium azide missing

00:12:28.380 --> 00:12:31.240
is consistent with a lethal dose
for one adult male.

00:12:31.360 --> 00:12:32.960
As a professor
of the chemistry department,

00:12:32.960 --> 00:12:34.960
she is precise in her measurements—

00:12:35.200 --> 00:12:36.390
which lends

00:12:36.470 --> 00:12:37.000
some credence

00:12:37.000 --> 00:12:39.390
to her claim
that she didn't kill Xiang Man.

00:12:39.390 --> 00:12:41.510
But since sodium azide
is a highly toxic substance,

00:12:41.510 --> 00:12:43.120
access to it should be
heavily restricted, right?

00:12:43.120 --> 00:12:44.050
Ordinary people

00:12:44.270 --> 00:12:45.800
shouldn't be able to get it.

00:12:47.630 --> 00:12:50.030
That's exactly the issue we're facing now.

00:12:54.230 --> 00:12:55.910
Why are you telling me all this?

00:12:55.910 --> 00:12:57.110
What's your purpose?

00:12:58.000 --> 00:13:00.320
I'm sharing these details to show you

00:13:00.720 --> 00:13:02.240
I have no ulterior motives toward you.

00:13:02.240 --> 00:13:02.930
Lu Yizhen.

00:13:05.760 --> 00:13:07.090
What are you doing here?

00:13:07.480 --> 00:13:08.720
What is wrong with you?

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:09.790
I just left you for a little while,

00:13:09.790 --> 00:13:11.130
and you've already managed
to stir up so much trouble!

00:13:11.130 --> 00:13:11.520
I...

00:13:11.550 --> 00:13:13.150
How am I supposed
to explain this to your parents?

00:13:13.150 --> 00:13:14.080
It's fine!

00:13:18.670 --> 00:13:20.000
You two know each other?

00:13:20.150 --> 00:13:20.790
No!

00:13:21.080 --> 00:13:23.410
What would I want with someone
from the police station?

00:13:23.410 --> 00:13:24.910
Nothing good ever comes
from associating with them.

00:13:24.910 --> 00:13:25.480
Let's go!

00:13:33.480 --> 00:13:34.150
Look,

00:13:34.240 --> 00:13:36.140
that cold case from over a decade ago
is back in the papers—

00:13:36.140 --> 00:13:38.140
with so many new details uncovered.

00:13:39.010 --> 00:13:39.080
[Missing Case Survivor Returns:
Lu Girl Seeks Revenge]

00:13:39.080 --> 00:13:40.010
Hey, who are you?

00:13:40.910 --> 00:13:41.870
My newspaper!

00:13:44.240 --> 00:13:45.360
Answer me!

00:13:47.370 --> 00:13:48.440
Give that back!

00:14:01.150 --> 00:14:02.080
I hate it

00:14:02.760 --> 00:14:04.690
when people interrupt my reading!

00:14:11.410 --> 00:14:13.410
The Survivor of the Missing Case...

00:14:14.910 --> 00:14:16.110
It's about that case.

00:14:20.130 --> 00:14:20.760
Lu Yizhen?

00:14:21.030 --> 00:14:21.790
So that's Lu Yizhen?

00:14:21.790 --> 00:14:23.150
Lu Yizhen! Lu Yizhen!

00:14:23.150 --> 00:14:25.510
Did you really live in that hellhole?

00:14:25.510 --> 00:14:26.960
How did you manage to escape?

00:14:26.960 --> 00:14:27.720
Lu Yizhen,

00:14:27.740 --> 00:14:29.340
how did you manage to escape?

00:14:29.750 --> 00:14:31.270
Did you have some kind

00:14:31.270 --> 00:14:33.800
of special relationship
with the kidnapper?

00:14:35.750 --> 00:14:36.630
This is a university campus!

00:14:36.630 --> 00:14:37.760
Stop this right now!

00:14:38.120 --> 00:14:39.120
Stop this right now!

00:14:39.120 --> 00:14:40.720
This is a university campus!

00:14:43.670 --> 00:14:44.440
Miss Lu.

00:14:44.600 --> 00:14:45.360
Miss Lu.

00:14:45.790 --> 00:14:46.550
Miss Lu!

00:14:47.320 --> 00:14:48.080
Miss Lu!

00:14:53.510 --> 00:14:54.910
The Republican Daily News
is selling well these days, right?

00:14:54.910 --> 00:14:55.510
Sure it is.

00:14:55.770 --> 00:14:56.840
Thanks to your tip

00:14:57.200 --> 00:14:58.120
on that case,

00:14:58.120 --> 00:15:00.780
our circulation
increased several times over.

00:15:00.980 --> 00:15:02.330
Just like you asked,

00:15:02.360 --> 00:15:04.790
I placed that piece
front and center on the front page.

00:15:04.790 --> 00:15:05.340
So,

00:15:06.120 --> 00:15:07.840
you'll keep feeding me

00:15:07.840 --> 00:15:09.320
exclusive case details from here on out,

00:15:09.320 --> 00:15:09.910
right?

00:15:10.720 --> 00:15:12.050
You'll be taken care of.

